author: Source: Inside Bay Area
title: Quinn: Why we cheer the new Silicon Valley patent office - Inside Bay Area
text:
It may seem a bit odd that in this digital age, Silicon Valley will celebrate this week the opening of a patent satellite office at San Jose City Hall. After all, a local patent office may not make much of a difference to large tech companies based here.
 Inside Bay Area.
